widgets_values: A small, cozy kitchen with wooden furniture and dim lighting from an old oil lamp. The room is cluttered but warm, with shelves filled with cooking utensils and ingredients. A young boy with weathered skin, wearing simple attire and a patched sail as a cloak, sits on a stool leaning slightly forward with his arms resting on the table. An older man with weathered skin and a stern but kind expression, wearing simple clothing typical of the area and having a patch on his sleeve, stands near the mending wall, looking at the boy.
